# {{lb|en|cycling}} A [[component]] used by the [[rider]] to control the gearing mechanisms and select the desired [[gear ratio]], usually connected to the [[derailleur]] by a [[mechanical]] [[actuation]] [[cable]].
# A [[spanner]] with an adjustable jaw size.
# {{lb|en|mining|historical}} A person employed to [[repair]] the [[horseway]]s and other [[passage]]s, and keep them [[unobstructed]].
# {{lb|en|US|Pennsylvania}} A [[switcher]] or [[shunter]]: a [[railroad]] [[locomotive]] used for [[shunt]]ing.
# {{lb|en|mythology|science fiction|fantasy}} A [[shape-shifter]], or a person or other being capable of changing their physical form.
# {{lb|en|erotica}} A genre of [[erotica]] focusing on [[lycanthrope]]s or other [[shapeshifter]]s, such as [[werewolves]].

